{"tid":107007,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"每人一套 電影中心上過既冷門戲","createTime":"2017-02-04T06:41:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-04T06:44:55.000Z","uid":80349,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6725399a68d05b1ecf857665a2915b36eba0cdf7","tid":107007,"uid":80349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T06:41:51.000Z","msg":"《白色恐懼》<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n《白色恐懼》是挑釁大導米高漢尼卡的新作，奪得了康城影展的金棕櫚大獎。電影是關於一條壓抑而隱晦的成魔之路。這裡所說的成魔，不僅是孩童長大成人後變成可怕的集體暴力的實踐者，而且是述說一個國家如何蛻變成一個不折不扣的「惡魔」。導演所反思的國家，不是別的國家，就是他自身所生於的德國。影片從頭到尾看似聚焦在一個小村莊所發生的種種怪事，但其實從影片的背景年份，或是當中一些伏筆及暗示，可以知道這要揭示的就是納粹的童年。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uimpx7kc\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuimpx7kc&h=56949376&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.filmcriticschina.org/?p=1164\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.filmcriticschina.org%2F%3Fp%3D1164&d=01EY%2BZdPKRb21p6QCrTOV0zHknCl6yzZyFDyfiap5zU%3D&h=8d4fcbab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.filmcriticschina.org/?p=1164</a>"},{"pid":"46cdaf4beab2428e2d139851232f8e9e5dae91bb","tid":107007,"uid":30084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T06:44:55.000Z","msg":"老而黎癲  the old man 乜今柒柒 好長唔記得左，<br />\n識小小歷史會笑到仆街"}]}